'''异烟酸甲酯'''是一种[[酯|酯]]类[[有机化合物|有机化合物]]，化学式为C<sub>7</sub>H<sub>7</sub>N<sub></sub>O<sub>2</sub>。

==合成==
异烟酸甲酯可由[[吡啶-4-甲醛|吡啶-4-甲醛]]和[[碘|碘]]、[[亚硝酸钠|亚硝酸钠]]在[[甲醇|甲醇]]中于70 °C反应得到；<ref name=Kiran />或由[[异烟酸|异烟酸]]和甲醇在[[硫酸|硫酸]]的存在下反应制得<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|volume=134|issue=27|language=en|issn=0002-7863|date=2012-07-11|pages=11104–11107|doi=10.1021/ja303951z|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/ja303951z|title=Photocatalytic Water Oxidation: Tuning Light-Induced Electron Transfer by Molecular Co 4 O 4 Cores|accessdate=2021-03-17|author=Serena Berardi, Giuseppina La Ganga, Mirco Natali, Irene Bazzan, Fausto Puntoriero, Andrea Sartorel, Franco Scandola, Sebastiano Campagna, Marcella Bonchio|archive-date=2022-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220308224643/https://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/ja303951z}}</ref>，其中，异烟酸也可转化为酰氯直接和醇反应得到酯。<ref>Attolino, Emanuele; De Marco, Alessandro; Allegrini, Pietro. Process for the preparation of 3-​(4-​pyridinyl)​propanol and intermediates useful in its synthesis. 2011. WO 2011138250 A1.</ref>

''N''-氧化吡啶-4-甲酸甲酯在[[雷尼镍|雷尼镍]]的催化下和[[甲酸铵|甲酸铵]]反应，也能得到异烟酸甲酯。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Synthetic Communications|volume=32|issue=11|language=en|issn=0039-7911|date=2002-01|pages=1681–1683|doi=10.1081/SCC-120004259|url=http://www.tandfonline.com/doi/abs/10.1081/SCC-120004259|title=A MILD AND SELECTIVE DEOXYGENATION OF N -OXIDES WITH AMMONIUM FORMATE AS A CATALYTIC HYDROGEN TRANSFER AGENT|accessdate=2021-03-17|author=Roman Balicki, Grzegorz Maciejewski}}</ref>

